com.identityx.clientSDK.credentialsProviders

Class PropFileCredentialsProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.identityx.clientSDK.credentialsProviders.PropFileCredentialsProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICredentialsProvider

    public class PropFileCredentialsProvider
extends Object
implements ICredentialsProvider
    Provides credentials from a properties file containing an un-encrypted shared secret. The credentials file is loaded from the class path. The file has to be a ".properties" file and contain the fields sharedKeyId, sharedKey, serviceUrl
